    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "On your life’s journey maybe you’re hurting,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just doesn’t seem like anyone cares;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus is waiting for you to open—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just call His name and He will be there!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What if I told you Somebody loves you;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He knows your name and He knows your case;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He will not judge but simply receive you;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He loves all men, and freely gives grace!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Jesus is Lord!” Oh, if you confess this,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And believe God raised Him from the grave;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If you believe and call upon Jesus,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus will come and you will be saved!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Simply call Jesus! Simply call Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O what a joy His name to declare;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If you are lonely, troubled or worried,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Call, “O Lord Jesus!”—and you’ll be saved!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
